":guilabel:`Doctor`, :guilabel:`Sra.`, :guilabel:`Srita.`, :guilabel:`Sr.` y "
":guilabel:`Profesor`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/service.rst:158
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: using the drop-down menu, select any tags that apply to "
